Class Waiter

java.lang.Object
hr.java.restaurant.model.Person
hr.java.restaurant.model.Waiter
public class Waiter extends Person
Represents a waiter at the restaurant. Inherits from the Person class. Contains information about the waiter's contract and bonus.
